<p class=3D"txt">There are more than 10 million possible combinations with =
PING irons, which are custom built to different color codes to fit players =
of varying sizes, swing tendencies and ball-flight preferences.&nbsp;From t=
hese measurements your fitter will build a club and begin the dynamic testi=
ng.<br>
&nbsp;</p>

